McKesson wins 5 - year , $ 1 . 0 bln contract . McKesson Corp on Thursday said its unit , McKesson Health Systems , has signed a contract with two health care companies that could generate over $ 1 . 0 billion in sales over the deal ' s five year life . The pact calls for McKesson to deliver pharmaceutical products to Capstone Pharmacy Services Inc and Stadtlanders Pharmacy . Capstone provides pharmacy services in 14 states to long - term care facilities containing about 120 , 000 beds . Stadtlanders provides specialty pharmaceutical care for individuals living with HIV / AIDS , organ transplants , oncology , infertility and other high - risk disease states . Capstone and Stadtlanders are affiliates of Counsel Corp , a provider of home health care , institutional pharmacy and specialty pharmacy services . 
